    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a major project or as a donor for spare parts. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a failing transmission and an engine that requires a complete overhaul to be roadworthy again. The body shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches and several dents, and the interior requires extensive restoration. While it is not currently in driving condition, it offers a wealth of usable components for someone restoring a similar model.",
