      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary vehicle preserved in showroom condition. This motorcar demonstrates an impeccable aesthetic and mechanical pedigree, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. With its flawless finish and pristine interior, it represents a premier opportunity for the sophisticated driver or collector. We invite serious inquiries for this peerless acquisition.",
