      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-quality specimen featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant with its factory-spec individual throttle bodies. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement using ARP hardware. The chassis is rock-solid with a reinforced rear subframe, and the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile shifts. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the factory paint depth remains consistent across all panels. It retains the original staggered 19-inch Style 67 wheels, and the variable M Differential Lock operates flawlessly. No pixel loss on the dash, no bolster wear\u2014just pure, high-revving mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
